What:
Bus controller board for the Blinkenlichten RGB LED controller


How:
* Blinkenlichten RGB LED controller (http://loetmeister.de/Elektronik/blinkenlichten_rgb_controller.htm) based on http://tim.cexx.org/?p=453
* Using Arduino NG with ATMEGA168


Features:
(1st running version, bear with me!)
- drive a bus of Blinkenlichten RGB LED controller (o rly? ;))
- interface to LCD (8*2)
- 3 buttons on ADC in (analog input)
- for all devices on the bus:
	moodlight mode (configurable speed)
	R, G ,B color select

	
Planned:
- Infrared input (like RC5)
- use EEPROM to save setup
- microphone input
- ...
